#artfashion for the #metoo #metoomovement.. 'LifeDress' by #aliciaframis, inflatable creations made out of airbags to protect you..Do swipe through. Seen as an #artinstallation at #artbasel2019 #Unlimited
Someone approach you a little too close, you just inflate you dress.. What do you think? 📷 @luxartasia /@couturenotebook

this makes me sad - they are beautiful but they are barriers - women already deal with so many barriers - better put these clothes on the offenders
Beautiful, unique and very safely for traveling!😉♥️
Airbags😂 I see it as playful, creative art and a challenge to construct.....not necessarily something to wear
I feel like it’s not respecting the movement
